id=nh-overlay-base
name=NetHunter Overlay Base (priv-app + F-Droid + repos)
version=v1.1
versionCode=2
author=ilyamen
description=Installs NetHunter, Terminal, KeX into /system/priv-app via Magisk overlay. Bundles F-Droid client + Privileged Extension and auto-adds NetHunter Store + IzzyOnDroid repos on first boot via fdroidrepos:// intents. Replaces deprecated NetHunter Store. addon.d hook for OTA survival. Reboot required after install.
